snippet.textDisplay: I love the image that he paints... a singer who lives down the valley... Sings about a day where he feels as if the atmosphere has become extremely quiet, which only means one thing and that is a storm is on its way...but then suddenly erupts with joy because he has not painted the full picture Infront of his audience... He has conveyed that the rain is falling but that it is a sunny day is what makes him happy... And the happiness can be felt from his voice when he touches that last note..." Sunny daayyyyy yiyeee"
